Class GadgetHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ovh.tgrhavoc.mvpgadgets.events.GadgetHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.event.Listener

    public class GadgetHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
    Handles the main events for this plugin. Events handled by this class: GadgetEvent - Executes the gadget (Calls Gadget#execute) PlayerJoinEvent - Adds the gadget selector to the player's inventory when they join PlayerInteractEvent - Calls the GadgetEvent event
    Author:
    Jordan Dalton
